<br>
Remember insurance companies only job is to make money. They will not settle claims easily even when their client is obviously at fault because they want to retain as much profit as possible. A lawyer can force them into settling when they realize the person is not going to be pressured into settling for less than it's worth or for complete medical coverage ect. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=23503" target="top">Cerranshaun Lightbringer</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
